('mcq', '{"prompt":"In Bar 3, the melody `gfed cdef` is best described as:","choices":["Conjunct (Stepwise)","Disjunct (Leaping)","onjunct (Stepwise) B) Disjunct (Leaping) C) Chromatic","isjunct (Leaping) C) Chromatic D) Atonal"],"explanation":null}'::jsonb, '{"correct":0}'::jsonb, 1, 'general'),
