('mcq', '{"prompt":"What material were harpsichord plectra originally made from?","choices":["Metal wire","Bird quills (feathers)","Wooden picks","Plastic strips"],"explanation":"Harpsichord plectra were traditionally made from bird quills, particularly crow or raven feathers, which provided the right flexibility and tone."}'::jsonb, '{"correct":1}'::jsonb, 1, 'general'),
